import React from 'react'
import { Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import {Row, Col, } from 'react-bootstrap'
import SecondScreenCard from './SecondScreenCard'
import India from '../Places/India'
import USA from '../Places/USA'
import axios from 'axios'


const SecondScreenitem = () => {

    const url = use

    return (
        <>
        <Container>
           <Row className="home-screen-container my-3 p-3 w-100" >
                {
                USA.map((secondscreen)=>(
                        <Col>
                            <SecondScreenCard
                                secondscreen={secondscreen}
                            />
                        </Col>
                    ))
                }
            </Row>
        </Container>
        </>
    )
}

export default SecondScreenitem
